DAY 9: loading…. @the_fcg #supremeteamboxing
DAY 10: this was actually on Friday late post. Back at it tomorrow morning. I'll take you up. Lol @the_fcg #supremeteamboxing
DAY 11: New Week! Same Grind! Get up and get it done.... @the_fcg #supremeteamboxing #shaketheblock #shakemiami

TURN IT UP! #BULLETPROOF RADIO IS ON!
@thebeatmiami #shaketheblock #shakemiami #wethebest #MMG
DAY 12: 03/28/23 YOU’LL NEVER KNOW THE VALUE OF A PERSON, UNTIL THEY BECOME A MEMORY... @the_fcg #supremeteamboxing #wethebest #mmg #shaketheblock #shakemiami
DAY 13: WANTS VS NEEDS. Sometimes we are so focused on what we want we miss the things we need. Keep giving your attention elsewhere, and you’ll lose what’s right in front of you.
Sometimes it’s the journey that teaches you a lot about your destination…
DAY 14: Thursday 03/30/23 move slower than I did the previous day. Still put in that work though. @the_fcg @thebeatmiami #supremeteamboxing #wethebest #mmg #shaketheblock #shakemiami
DAY 15: this was Friday 03/31/23 currently I’m in Raleigh NC thinking about how I’m going to get to the gym Monday when I’m traveling in the morning
Big Thank you to @playabowlsdavie @playabowls for the special delivery today for the @thebeatmiami fam!!! Right on time for me after my workout this morning!!

DAY 16: just because I haven’t posted heavy this week doesn’t mean I wasn’t working. So day 16 wasn’t a gym workout. But between the 2days of #Dreamvile I walked 34000 steps an approximate 12 miles. You don’t have to be in the gym to be healthy just get out there and move.
DAY 17: Tuesday 04/04/23 out Work and out perform! Get past the hardest part and that’s showing up. @the_fcg #supremeteamboxing @thebeatmiami #wethebest #mmg

DAY 18: Wednesday 04/05/23 My Future came and worked out with me today. True inspiration! Plus she’s learning how to know you broke boys out when she gets older. @the_fcg #supremeteamboxing  @thebeatmiami #wethebest #mmg
S/o to my trainer @flaco5125 @the_fcg #supremeteamboxing support the real ones

DAY 19: Thursday 04/06/23 I didn’t come this far, just to come this far… gotta keep going. A task with out a goal is pointless. @the_fcg #supremeteamboxing  @thebeatmiami #wethebest #mmg #shaketheblock #shakemiami podcast coming soon…
DAY 20: Friday 04/07/23 Trying to get caught up with these post. Bear with me @the_fcg #supremeteamboxing  @thebeatmiami #wethebest #mmg #shaketheblock #shakemiami podcast coming soon…

FIJI X DJ BULLETPROOF

As one of South Florida’s premier Brands And vibe curators:
Fiji and DJ Bulletproof are committed to providing exceptional party experiences while prioritizing the safety and comfort of our valued guests. It is with regret that we must announce the postponement of DJ Bulletproof’s 10th-anniversary event, which was scheduled to be hosted by Shenseea. This decision was reached after careful consideration of the approaching cold front that may cause temperatures to drop significantly, making it unsuitable for an outdoor event.

We express our deepest gratitude for your unwavering support, and we are determined to make it up to you by hosting a fabulous makeup event. We are also pleased to inform you that all presold tickets will be refunded via the original form of payment.

We apologize for any inconvenience caused and pledge to continue delivering unforgettable experiences that meet the highest standards of safety and comfort for our guests.
